<TEXT>&#2;<DATELINE>2006-01-05</DATELINE><TITLE>Virology 50th Anniversary Special Issue: A Publisher's Note</TITLE><BODY>A Publishers Note introduces this special issue, commemorating Virology's 50th birthday, with a look back at its prestigious history, and the scientific progress that has been made in the field since the launch of the journal in 1954. It provides a list of the top 100 most-cited papers published in the journal to date.&#3;</BODY></TEXT>